General Manager Operations
Job Seekers
|
|
what:
where:
Dubai
Retail giant based from Dubai seek General Manager to lead and grow their operations across the MiddleEast; the role is based in Dubai so the successful candidate will have to relocate for this opportunity. The business is going through a fantastic period of growth at the moment so this is a good time to join them.
Key Responsibilities:
Driving sales and KPI’S across the business
Experienced in dealing with large head count
In depth knowledge of the retail environment e.g. logistics and warehousing
Complete duties with customer focus in mind in line with customer behaviour and expectations
Ensuring all strategic tools are in place and reflect the seasons trading performance
Inventory management
Applicants need to have existing retail operations experience from preferably a large format retail background and be able to demonstrate their attention to detail and analytical skills. It is essential for the candidate to be highly motivated and organised with a naturally tenacious personality. As mentioned, should relocation not be something you can consider the unfortunately, the role is not for you. This job was originally posted as
